{"tid":1739733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【女督察難產】分娩後離世男嬰留醫ICU","createTime":"2019-11-19T16:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T17:16:36.000Z","uid":48,"like":53,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2eb708142bed6d1598e2c85e7f3ba67d6cba80","tid":1739733,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"33歲女高級督察黃麗瑩在年初三(本周一)，在伊利沙伯醫院待產時，出現羊水栓塞及子宮大量出血，可憐她誕下男嬰後離世，初生男嬰現時仍留醫在深切治療部，與死神搏鬥，命懸一線。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，黃麗瑩高級督察生前駐守邊界警區刑事調查隊，11年擢升為督察，她與丈夫居於上水紀律部隊宿舍，過着甜蜜生活。直至去年，她懷有第一胎，已定期進行產前檢查，丈夫更悉心照料不離左右。在懷孕期間，兩人已買定嬰兒床，迎接愛兒誕生，豈料，她產子後死亡，無法見到愛兒睡在新床。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20140205/52159014?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140205%2F52159014%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=a4841e01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140205%2F52159014%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=0a012e09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20140205/52159014?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"62a23093306c62958cfa2d8dea0fd0818e839d21","tid":1739733,"uid":58167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2953852acaab50f15f898f38dee06ee12247190d","tid":1739733,"uid":58552,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"唔好拎耐d嘅新聞"}